#size
absolute
- pixel: px
- milimeter: mm
- centimeter: cm
- point: pt
- pica: pc (12pt)
- inch: in (6pc)
relative
- font-size: em
- font-size: rem (root)
- parent: %
- device: vw (width)
- device: vh (height)
- device: vmin
- device: vmax
